      <title>特斯拉马斯克预测明年人工智能将比最聪明的人类更聪明</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/teslas-musk-predicts-ai-will-be-smarter-than-smartest-human-next-year-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉首席执行官埃隆·马斯克周一预测，到明年或 2026 年，人工智能的发展可能会比最聪明的人类还要聪明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/teslas-musk-predicts-ai-will-be-smarter-than-smartest-human-next-year-2024-04-08/</guid>
